role_name,biz_unit,is_admin,notes
*admin,*,yes,Users in roles ending with admin are able to see all bunits and administer the app
*roles_containing*,Business Unit 5,no,Users in roles matching a string can only see bunit5
*roles_ending_with,Business Unit 4,no,Users in roles ending with a string can only see bunit4
role1,Business Unit 1,no,Users in role1 can only see bunit1
role2,Business Unit 2,no,Users in role2 can only see bunit2
role3,"Business Unit 1,Business Unit 2",no,Users in role3 can see both bunit1 and bunit2
roles_starting_with*,"ABC*,XYZ",no,Users in roles starting with a string can see all bunits starting with ABC and XYZ
